      "span_text": "Little data on the association between fatty liver and hepatic energy metabolism are currently available; Sharma et al. reported that using hepatic 31 P-MR spectroscopy, the fasting relative content of high-energy phosphates (HEPs) was altered in obese individuals with NAFLD than in controls."
